{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775899777662,"sessionID":"ses_28420c30cffepE7vemUlRXG8Kj","part":{"id":"prt_d7be01830001gdE6E5dDHN2mO8","messageID":"msg_d7be009a3001GDXgKlLWwBBoMH","sessionID":"ses_28420c30cffepE7vemUlRXG8Kj","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_tool-c3508d407ba042ee883eb54888c0cdea","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"find /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/agentcube -name \"*.md\" -type f","description":"Find markdown files in agentcube"},"output":"","metadata":{"output":"","exit":0,"description":"Find markdown files in agentcube","truncated":false},"title":"Find markdown files in agentcube","time":{"start":1775899777643,"end":1775899777661}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775899777669,"sessionID":"ses_28420c30cffepE7vemUlRXG8Kj","part":{"id":"prt_d7be01a50001OpVr5KTtZ872aK","messageID":"msg_d7be009a3001GDXgKlLWwBBoMH","sessionID":"ses_28420c30cffepE7vemUlRXG8Kj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-0cb168b1a9994632a679f6d5acf4bebb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Design: AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: 本文档描述了为 agentcube 项目中 `pkg/router`、`pkg/store` 和 `pkg/picod` 模块编写全面单元测试的技术实现设计。这些模块构成了系统的核心组件，负责路由、存储和代码执行功能。\n6: \n7: ## 目标\n8: \n9: 1. 为 router、store、picod 模块提供全面的单元测试覆盖\n10: 2. 确保代码质量和可靠性\n11: 3. 提供可维护的测试基础设施\n12: 4. 遵循 Go 测试最佳实践\n13: \n14: ## 架构\n15: \n16: ### 整体架构\n17: \n18: ```\n19: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n20: │                          router                                 │\n21: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n22: │  │   handlers   │  │  middleware  │  │  session_mgr │         │\n23: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n24: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n25: │  │   jwt_mgr    │  │resource_cache│  │ informer_mgr │         │\n26: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n27: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n28:                               │\n29:                               ▼\n30: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n31: │                           store                                 │\n32: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n33: │  │ store_redis  │  │store_valkey  │  │    codec     │         │\n34: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n35: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n36:                               │\n37:                               ▼\n38: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n39: │                          picod                                  │\n40: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n41: │  │   handlers   │  │  middleware  │  │  auth_mgr    │         │\n42: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n43: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n44: │  │ workspace_mgr│  │ status_rptr  │  │informr_mgr   │         │\n45: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n46: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ### 模块职责\n50: \n51: #### Router 模块\n52: - **handlers.go**: HTTP 请求处理逻辑\n53: - **middleware.go**: 中间件（认证、限流、日志、监控）\n54: - **session_manager.go**: 会话管理和沙盒生命周期\n55: - **jwt.go**: JWT 令牌生成和验证\n56: - **resource_cache.go**: Kubernetes 资源缓存\n57: - **informer_manager.go**: Kubernetes informer 管理\n58: - **server.go**: HTTP 服务器启动和配置\n59: \n60: #### Store 模块\n61: - **store.go**: 存储接口定义\n62: - **store_redis.go**: Redis 存储实现\n63: - **store_valkey.go**: ValKey 存储实现\n64: - **codec.go**: 数据序列化/反序列化\n65: - **singleton.go**: 存储实例管理\n66: \n67: #### Picod 模块\n68: - **handlers.go**: 文件操作和命令执行处理\n69: - **middleware.go**: 认证中间件\n70: - **auth.go**: 认证管理器\n71: - **workspace_manager.go**: 工作空间管理\n72: - **status_reporter.go**: 状态报告\n73: - **informer.go**: Kubernetes informer 集成\n74: - **server.go**: HTTP 服务器\n75: \n76: ## 数据结构\n77: \n78: ### Router 模块数据结构\n79: \n80: #### 核心类型\n81: \n82: ```go\n83: // Server 主服务器结构\n84: type Server struct {\n85:     config         *Config\n86:     engine         *gin.Engine\n87:     httpServer     *http.Server\n88:     sessionManager SessionManager\n89:     storeClient    store.Store\n90:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n91:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n92:     handler        *Handler\n93:     limiter        *ConcurrencyLimiter\n94:     metrics        *Metrics\n95:     mu             sync.RWMutex\n96: }\n97: \n98: // Handler HTTP 处理器\n99: type Handler struct {\n100:     sessionManager SessionManager\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 979. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Design: AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n## 概述\n\n本文档描述了为 agentcube 项目中 `pkg/router`、`pkg/store` 和 `pkg/picod` 模块编写全面单元测试的技术实现设计。这些模块构成了系统的核心组件，负责路由、存储和代码执行功能。\n\n## 目标\n\n1. 为 router、store、picod 模块提供全面的单元测试覆盖\n2. 确保代码质量和可靠性\n3. 提供可维护的测试基础设施\n4. 遵循 Go 测试最佳实践\n\n## 架构\n\n### 整体架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                          router                                 │","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775899777646,"end":1775899777666}}}}
