{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775899883099,"sessionID":"ses_28420c30cffepE7vemUlRXG8Kj","part":{"id":"prt_d7be1b628001aqD70bXdTLD7Lz","messageID":"msg_d7be1a638001X1m04zgBm31dMu","sessionID":"ses_28420c30cffepE7vemUlRXG8Kj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-5b8c518f2a074f37b3cb03498ed520fe","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/agentcube/design.md","limit":50},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/agentcube/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Design: AR-043 — AgentCube Architecture Design and API Documentation\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native AI agent runtime platform that provides tools for building, deploying, and managing AI agent workloads. The platform consists of a Python SDK, CLI tools, and Kubernetes custom resources that together enable a complete agent development lifecycle.\n6: \n7: ## Architecture\n8: \n9: ### High-Level Architecture\n10: \n11: ```\n12: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n13: │                         Developer Layer                              │\n14: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐              │\n15: │  │   Python SDK │  │   CLI Tools  │  │  kubectl plg │              │\n16: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘              │\n17: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n18:                               │\n19:                               ▼\n20: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n21: │                      AgentCube Platform                              │\n22: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n23: │  │                    Control Plane                              │  │\n24: │  │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐      │  │\n25: │  │  │ Workload Mgr │  │ Controller   │  │ CRD Manager  │      │  │\n26: │  │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘      │  │\n27: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n28: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n29: │  │                    Data Plane                                 │  │\n30: │  │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐      │  │\n31: │  │  │    Router    │  │    Picod     │  │ Session Store│      │  │\n32: │  │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘      │  │\n33: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n34: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n35:                               │\n36:                               ▼\n37: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n38: │                      Kubernetes Cluster                              │\n39: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐              │\n40: │  │ AgentRuntime │  │CodeInterpreter│  │Agent Workload│              │\n41: │  │    CRDs      │  │    CRDs       │  │   Pods       │              │\n42: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘              │\n43: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n44: ```\n45: \n46: ### Component Architecture\n47: \n48: #### Python SDK Layer\n49: \n50: ```\n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 1007. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Design: AR-043 — AgentCube Architecture Design and API Documentation\n\n## Overview\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native AI agent runtime platform that provides tools for building, deploying, and managing AI agent workloads. The platform consists of a Python SDK, CLI tools, and Kubernetes custom resources that together enable a complete agent development lifecycle.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Architecture\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         Developer Layer                              │\n│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐              │\n│  │   Python SDK │  │   CLI Tools  │  │  kubectl plg │              │\n│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/agentcube/design.md","time":{"start":1775899883075,"end":1775899883096}}}}
